{"title":"Wizard Works’ Wiz Viz is Back!","link":"https://theradavist.com/wizard-works-wiz-viz/","date":1729864074000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_002.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_002.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_002.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_002.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>UK-based <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/wizard-works/\" target=\"_blank\">Wizard Works</a> brought back its highly reflective <a href=\"https://www.wizard.works/wiz-viz/\" target=\"_blank\">Wiz Viz collection</a> for winter riding…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Shazam_002.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Shazam_002.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Shazam_002.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Shazam_002.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Shazam_001.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Shazam_001.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Shazam_001.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Shazam_001.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>This special line of bags feature German made, reflective dot Cordura that looks black during the day but when lights hit the fabric, it lights up.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Lil_Presto_002.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Lil_Presto_002.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Lil_Presto_002.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Lil_Presto_002.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Lil_Presto_001.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Lil_Presto_001.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Lil_Presto_001.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Lil_Presto_001.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>This year Wizard Works’ entire Core Range of bike bags gets the Wiz Viz treatment making it easy to match any bags you already own from the previous collections. Because matching is almost as important as being safe.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Forres_002.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Forres_002.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Forres_002.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Forres_002.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Forres_001.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Forres_001.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Forres_001.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/Wizard_Works_Wiz_Viz_Forres_001.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Wiz Viz is available Friday Oct 25th until daylight savings returns in March 2025, at which point it will disappear for the summer months, returning the following autumn.</p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.wizard.works/wiz-viz/\" target=\"_blank\">Wizard Works</a>!</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/wizard-works-wiz-viz/\">Wizard Works’ Wiz Viz is Back!</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"ad14010c3845c22b5cbc13a74bf278b0dcdac6b5dcbc38300d049f1aed0dae63","category":"Cycling"}